        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到Core和Ctee的命名有点特殊——您写的是swaparoo<brdeployer和swaparoo<brcommittee，这里的<br是换行符的意思吗？我需要确认显示格式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Ctee",
        "swaparoo<brdeployer",
        "swaparoo<brcommittee"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Core显示为swaparoo然后换行brdeployer，Ctee也是swaparoo换行brcommittee。这样标注清楚它们的合约角色。另外流程上，Core要先调用Zoe的startInstance来启动诊断引擎。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Zoe",
        "startInstance",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，已添加。接下来Zoe要启动HIPAA Vault对吧？我看到Ctee会返回Vault实例给Zoe，然后Zoe再回传给Core。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Zoe",
        "Ctee",
        "start",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。但下一步有个细节：Core要通过Ctee获取投票邀请，具体是调用E(HealthTech_PatientRecords).getVoterInvitations，传入诊断引擎参数。这里E表示PatientRecords合约的实例。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Core",
        "Ctee",
        "E(HealthTech_PatientRecords)",
        "getVoterInvitations",
        "HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "收到。那Ctee返回给Core的是什么？我注意到您之前提到LabAnalyzer，但流程里似乎是要返回投票邀请列表？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ctee",
        "Core",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "这里我修正一下——Ctee返回的是[HealthTech_LabAnalyzer]，表示实验室分析器的列表，不是直接返回邀请。然后Core再单独给Voter1发invitationV1。这是两步：先获取分析器配置，再定向发邀请。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ctee",
        "Core",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "Core",
        "Voter1",
        "invitationV1"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "清楚了，两步分离：Ctee→Core返回LabAnalyzer数组，然后Core→V1发送具体邀请。整个流程是：启动引擎→创建Vault→获取分析器→发送邀请。我加上自动编号，确认无误。",
